Package: SSFairnessAudit
Type: Package
Title: Semi-Supervised Fairness Auditing for Predictive Models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jianhui Gao
Maintainer: Jianhui Gao <jianhui.gao@mail.utoronto.ca>
Description: Provides tools for auditing group fairness metrics in
    supervised and semi-supervised settings. The package includes fairness
    estimators, model selection and basis construction utilities, influence
    curve variance estimation, and synthetic data generation for simulation
    studies.
